          "tweet_id": "2073945036509909294",
          "original_text": "i write a prompt with the role and output requirements, then ask claude code in natural language to use dynamic workflows. this feature lets cc orchestrate hundreds of agents map-reduce style: it spins them all up in parallel, each researching one candidate, then merges everything into a single list and emails it to me when it’s done. you can inspect the workflow json it generates, but i usually don’t unless something goes wrong",
          "created_at": "2026-07-06T01:40:03+00:00",
          "like_count": 12,
          "retweet_count": 0,
          "reply_count": 2
        },
